Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.15,0:00:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到出神陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.19,0:00:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 愛到懊惱萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.03,0:00:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我什麼也不怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.57,0:00:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳 無法忘記妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.54,0:00:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,風兒硬是拆開\N我們纏綿甜蜜的吻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.75,0:00:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,面對無法停止的熾熱心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.09,0:00:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請不要流淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.96,0:00:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令人無法討厭的冷漠態度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.17,0:00:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,見不到面令我痛苦萬分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.14,0:01:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳鬱悶不樂的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.31,0:01:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,令我心碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.32,0:01:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.39,0:01:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我愛妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.35,0:01:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.05,0:01:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.22,0:01:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎有沒有來你這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.82,0:01:52.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.59,0:01:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有看到的話要逮住他喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.46,0:01:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸,出了什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.26,0:02:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸在生什麼氣啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎怎麼了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.90,0:02:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.65,0:02:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.73,0:03:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,#44  賢太郎也嚇到臉色發青?\N四谷恐怖的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.47,0:03:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下星期開始應該就能照往常一樣\N去妳家上課了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.41,0:03:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要太勉強喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.04,0:03:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好無聊喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.95,0:03:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,代我向爸爸問好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.45,0:03:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回家路上小心點喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.42,0:03:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方便的話,一起吃晚飯好嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.63,0:03:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我連郁子的份都做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.00,0:03:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那我就不客氣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.42,0:04:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.78,0:04:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起喔\N不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.45,0:04:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我知道了\N你被媽媽罵了,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.76,0:04:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我偷藏了一張考卷\N被媽媽發現了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.62,0:04:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽說考不好沒關係\N可是藏起來就是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.46,0:04:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這也難怪她會生氣\N可是,你居然因為被罵而哭啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.63,0:04:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢\N我才不是為了那種事哭呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟妳說\N妳不能說出去喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.77,0:04:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.78,0:04:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳能保證妳絕對不會說出去嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.04,0:05:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我保證
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.02,0:05:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好心理準備了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.90,0:05:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(東京奧運會)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.77,0:05:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四號房的四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.34,0:05:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟以前一樣都沒變耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,東京奧運是幾年前的事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.54,0:05:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.74,0:05:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.75,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.85,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,是軍人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.58,0:05:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳仔細看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.22,0:05:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,騙人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.26,0:05:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一張更可怕喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.73,0:05:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一張
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一刻館上樑儀式紀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.20,0:06:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊,我看過這張照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.64,0:06:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鐘台後面的小孩\N是我叔叔小時候的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.01,0:06:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.63,0:06:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在樓閣裡找到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.50,0:06:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事,惡作劇做不出來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.17,0:06:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是,這樣四谷不就成了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.24,0:06:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成了什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.11,0:06:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.71,0:06:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係,妳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.48,0:07:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣大概又會被罵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.33,0:07:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好遠喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了,我忍不住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.44,0:07:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說吸血鬼\N或是穿越時空來的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.31,0:07:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或是長生不老的仙人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.69,0:08:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看了,對不對?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.19,0:08:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是十字光線嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.70,0:08:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不懂你說什麼\N這是十字架喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.20,0:08:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西對我無效!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.77,0:08:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要我泡杯茶給妳喝?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.40,0:08:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.58,0:08:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賢太郎他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.34,0:08:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了,我不想發牢騷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.35,0:09:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代也說\N賢太郎最近怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.69,0:09:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出了什麼事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.52,0:09:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代也這麼說?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.89,0:09:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我稍微罵了一下賢太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.93,0:09:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後來他居然變得神經兮兮的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.39,0:09:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我平常明明不是這樣教育他的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.17,0:09:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,我是音無
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.57,0:09:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,郁子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.84,0:09:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照片有什麼問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.05,0:09:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來還有那種照片啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.25,0:09:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.62,0:09:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算四谷真的不太像人\N不過應該不可能吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道四谷的名字嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.89,0:09:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是“龜吉”\N不過,要唸成“鶴次”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.90,0:09:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我說是“富士”\N但是要唸成“河田町”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.50,0:09:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來兩個都是假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.10,0:09:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔細想想\N我們對四谷的事,真的一無所知
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.08,0:10:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說得也是\N只知道他喜歡偷窺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.98,0:10:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩人在這裡幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.59,0:10:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.89,0:10:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,教練說有事找我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.59,0:10:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教練?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.86,0:10:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯\N為什麼會有那麼詭異的人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.60,0:10:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從以前就覺得很不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.20,0:10:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音無小姐\N這次一定要拆穿他的真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.80,0:10:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拆…拆穿真面目?\N這樣會不會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.17,0:10:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳太心軟了,仔細聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.91,0:10:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹怎麼會在這裡?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.68,0:10:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.98,0:10:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,你們兩個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.71,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別人講話的時候要專心聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有必要做到這樣嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.98,0:10:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,那你的意思是什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.89,0:10:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你認為只要找四谷叫他說明\N他就會乖乖地回答嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.93,0:10:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是沒有這麼想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.60,0:10:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧,沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是應該自然一點…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.63,0:10:57.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我說了要裝作自然一點\N悄悄跟蹤四谷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.04,0:11:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到具體的線索\N然後查出他究竟是何方神聖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不對?音無小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.71,0:11:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.04,0:11:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉,我不參加\N我不太適合參加這種的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.85,0:11:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就沒辦法,我不會強迫妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.19,0:11:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是,請不要把這件事告訴四谷…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.12,0:11:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦,我會保密的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.79,0:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.43,0:11:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼來討論具體的作戰計劃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.46,0:11:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好安靜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.46,0:12:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安靜的茶碗蒸、栗子飯\N也有安靜的牛肉燴飯喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.17,0:12:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太安靜了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.49,0:12:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代真的有起床嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.40,0:12:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.60,0:12:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想四谷今天會在幾點出門呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.07,0:12:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該不會偏偏今天不出門吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.57,0:12:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳就稍微冷靜一點嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.74,0:12:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我?我很冷靜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.38,0:12:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我去叫五代起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.59,0:12:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早…早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.66,0:13:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,我出門了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.40,0:13:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.30,0:13:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣會跟丟他的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天就算了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.54,0:13:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那怎麼行呢\N因為三鷹也在等我們啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.47,0:13:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,快叫五代起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,那妳出發吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.78,0:13:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.28,0:13:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫五代起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.79,0:13:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.63,0:13:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.40,0:13:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有東西放在玄關忘了拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.04,0:13:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快點!快點!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.67,0:13:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大嬸,等一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.79,0:14:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,管理員,管理員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.94,0:14:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開始在進行了,開始在進行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.30,0:14:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,氣氛好詭異喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.77,0:14:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷的私生子嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.58,0:15:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.98,0:15:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼,老師再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.65,0:15:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.63,0:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.27,0:15:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.07,0:15:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,時鐘坡下面的巴士站是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.14,0:15:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我立刻通知三鷹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.15,0:16:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,五代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.65,0:16:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正想去柏青哥店打小鋼珠\N消磨一下時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.29,0:16:23.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是一個人去又有點無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能在這裡碰到你\N也算是一種緣分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.96,0:16:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣?一起去吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.37,0:16:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請你要買小彈珠給我喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.30,0:16:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代搞砸了,三鷹也被甩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.34,0:16:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來輪到妳出場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.07,0:16:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.61,0:16:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非得扮成這樣不可嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.58,0:16:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼問?很適合妳啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.02,0:16:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟我年輕的時候好像喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.26,0:18:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,財團法人\N國際難民救助隊極東分部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂,三鷹教練嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.14,0:18:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情我聽說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.30,0:18:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬上去跟管理員會合\N地點是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.05,0:19:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓你看到這付醜樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.32,0:19:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不會啊,蠻有味道的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.85,0:19:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.56,0:19:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趴下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.63,0:19:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他要去哪裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.03,0:19:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次換我來跟蹤他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.43,0:19:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳去剛才的大樓\N打聽四谷的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.54,0:19:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要平安回來喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.84,0:19:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太誇張了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.65,0:20:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過說來真巧啊\N你怎麼會在這裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.76,0:20:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我出來散散步\N倒是你怎麼會在這裡呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.63,0:20:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你問我嗎?\N我是下班回家路上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.93,0:20:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦,下班啊\N你在做什麼工作呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.70,0:20:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.64,0:20:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賣鬆緊帶的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,譬如說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.31,0:20:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被稱作老師的人\N不見得全都是教書的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.58,0:20:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出入某個團體的人\N不見得全都是那裡的職員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.59,0:20:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又例如
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.86,0:20:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秦始皇蓋了萬里長城\N但他卻不是建築工人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.83,0:20:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨身帶著鬆緊帶的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.16,0:20:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有可能是區公所\N戶籍課的職員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.44,0:21:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說到職業這門學問\N真的很深奧啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.31,0:21:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,我差不多該走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.55,0:21:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.65,0:21:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,答案是三個字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.02,0:21:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是警察在跟蹤監視\N嫌疑犯的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.56,0:21:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣沒錯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.76,0:21:29.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你事前全都知道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.87,0:21:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.14,0:21:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三鷹的作戰計劃雖然失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.91,0:21:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡面難道沒有什麼\N可以成為線索的照片嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.91,0:21:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這會不會只是合成照片?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.75,0:21:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以四谷的個性來說\N很有可能做這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.98,0:21:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我家也有那張\N上樑儀式的照片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.52,0:21:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爺爺說\N他根本不認識四谷這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:58.80,0:22:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,於淺草國際劇場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.20,0:22:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地下鐵通車紀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.74,0:22:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日德防共協定紀念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.11,0:22:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野狗小黑要來了?\N(1931年雜誌連載漫畫)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.33,0:22:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家族?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.70,0:22:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對,四谷先生說那是\N他以為已經遺失的家族相簿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.94,0:22:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是他伯父
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:45.01,0:22:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是他爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:48.95,0:22:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有,這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.95,0:22:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是他爺爺…嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.35,0:22:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對,他說一刻館的歷史\N就是四谷家的歷史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.19,0:22:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.00,0:23:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擋住!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.24,0:23:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,五代說他期末考到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.78,0:23:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有用,沒有用\N就算現在抱佛腳也沒有用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.68,0:24:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們的宴會要被禁止呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.22,0:24:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.88,0:24:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「震驚的重大宣言?\N響子對五代愛的告白」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.75,0:24:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦!不會吧?\N誰知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.17,0:24:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們互相凝視時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.63,0:24:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就會有一道奇妙的旋律\N在心中迴響著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:33.68,0:24:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無法用言語來表達愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:40.46,0:24:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只好彈奏起了鋼琴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.96,0:24:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請把夢丟進來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.27,0:24:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為我測量一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.07,0:24:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愛有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.84,0:25:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用輕觸的嘴唇演奏著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.05,0:25:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平靜的合聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:12.09,0:25:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使擁抱著妳依然惆悵滿懷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:18.16,0:25:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夢見了Fantasy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:25.30,0:25:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開啟了只有我們兩人\N才看得見的門扉Fantasy
